**–¢–≤–æ–π –û—Ç–≤–µ—Ç:**

```
üé® **Prompt:**
A cyberpunk scientist in a cluttered, high-tech laboratory, meticulously adjusting a holographic interface. The scene is rendered with the same hyper-realistic digital painting style and vibrant neon color palette as the reference, featuring dramatic volumetric lighting from glowing screens and deep, atmospheric shadows.

üö´ **Negative Prompt:**
low quality, blurry, deformed anatomy, extra fingers, poorly drawn hands, cartoonish, watermark, signature, text, dull colors.

üì∑ **Camera & Lighting:**
Shot with a 35mm lens at f/2.8, creating a moderate depth of field that keeps the scientist sharp while the background blurs into colorful bokeh. Lighting is dominated by cool, blue-hued neon from the holograms acting as the key light, with warm, practical lights on equipment providing fill and contrast.

ü™Ñ **Style & Post-Processing:**
Hyper-realistic digital painting with a cinematic color grade. Strong influence of neon-noir aesthetic. Mood is focused and immersive. Fine details and sharp focus on intricate technology and facial expression, with a slight chromatic aberration effect for a techy feel.
